description:
Roles & Responsibilities


Responsibilities:
Perform budget variance analysis and report to Local Management and Group HQ;
Month end consolidation at country, region and group level;
Improve and automate financial reports;
Work with senior management to define and track key performance indicators to support business decisions;
Coordinate and support future budget preparation;
Conduct market and competitor analysis;
Other ad hoc requests for analysis as requested from senior management.

Requirements :
Bachelor Degree in Accountancy, Data Analytics or relevant field with at least 4 years of working experiences;
Preferably with external audit background and familiar with SAGE system;
Strong technical knowledge.

Interested parties to send their resume with a photo to grouphr@transnational-grp.com
